48	// Routes authenticated+authorized inbound requests to per-action handlers.
49	// The listener already ran all five inbound gates (method, content-type,
50	// auth, cross-session, body-size fail-fast) before we're invoked. The
51	// dispatcher's job is strictly: pick a handler by (method, path), read the
52	// body, run the handler, write the response.
53	//
54	// Two handler shapes:
55	//   - ACTIONS (POST/GET with synchronous response): readJsonBody → handler
56	//     → write response. Handler returns {status, body}.
57	//   - EVENTS (POST, fire-and-forget 202): readJsonBody → validator →
